snippet: Tirunesh Dibaba won the women’s two-mile run at the New Balance Indoor Grand Prix in Boston, and Mary Cain of Bronxville, N.Y., set a record for high schoolers and finished third.
abstract: Tirunesh Dibaba wins women’s two-mile run at New Balance Indoor Grand Prix in Boston, and Mary Cain, who finished third, sets record for high schoolers at 9 minutes 38.68 seconds.
lead_paragraph: Tirunesh Dibaba won the women’s two-mile run at the New Balance Indoor Grand Prix in Boston, and Mary Cain of Bronxville, N.Y., set a record for high schoolers and finished third.

headline.main: Ethiopian Wins at 2 Miles in Boston
